data: {"p":"response/fragments/-3/results","v":[{"url":"https://www.accuweather.com/zh/cn/guangzhou/102255/air-quality-index/102255","title":"广州, 广东省, 中国空气质量指数 | AccuWeather","snippet":"空气质量量表 ... 空气质量对大多数人来说是可接受的。然而 ... 广州的当前空气质量 极好 危险 极好 有利 差 不健康 很不健康 危险 ## 24小时空气质量预报","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/accuweather.com","site_name":"AccuWeather","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"http://sthjj.gz.gov.cn/zwgk/hjgb/","title":"广州市生态环境局网站","snippet":"2026年1月广州市环境空气质量状况 2026-02-24 广州市白云区2024年度生态环境统计公报 2026-01-27 2025年12月广州市环境空气质量状况 2026-01-22 广州市2024年排放源统计公报","cite_index":null,"published_at":null,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/gz.gov.cn","site_name":"广州市生态环境局","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"http://cenews.com.cn/news.html?aid=1770007","title":"从“广州蓝”到“全运蓝”，广州以治气硬功守牢生态颜值——中国环境网","snippet":"2025年，广州AQI达标率达93.4%，连续3年超九成；PM2.5平均浓度降至21.5微克/立方米，在国家中心城市中保持最优。尤其在十五运会举办期间...","cite_index":null,"published_at":1771948800.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/cenews.com.cn","site_name":"中国环境网","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"http://www.zx24.com/aqi/guangdong-guangzhou.html","title":"广州空气污染：实时空气质量指数（AQI）","snippet":"空气质量指数 | 污染级别 | 对健康的影响 | 建议采取措施 ---|---|---|--- 0-50 | 优 | 空气质量令人满意，基本无空气污染，对健康没有危害 | 各类人群可多参加户外活动，多呼吸一下清新的空气。","cite_index":null,"published_at":1774713600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/zx24.com","site_name":"zx24.com","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"http://vlife.src.weather.com.cn/maqi/101280101.shtml","title":"广州空气质量指数AQI--中国天气网","snippet":"优 良 轻度 中度 重度 严重 PM2.5 PM10 CO NO2 SO2 O3 单位:μg/m3（CO为mg/m3）","cite_index":null,"published_at":null,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/weather.com.cn","site_name":"天气网","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"http://www.yuexiu.gov.cn/yxdt/rdzt/zdlyxxgk/hjbh/kqhjxx/","title":"广州市越秀区人民政府门户网站","snippet":"2026年1月广州市环境空气质量状况 2026-03-04 2025年12月广州市环境空气质量状况 2026-01-27 2025年11月广州市环境空气质量状况 2025-12-16 2025年10月广州市环境空气质量状况","cite_index":null,"published_at":null,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/yuexiu.gov.cn","site_name":"广州市越秀区人民政府","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"http://pc.weathercn.com/weather/102255/?partner=20000010%d0%93%d2%93%d0%96%e2%80%99%d0%93%d3%ae%d0%92%d0%88%d0%93%d2%93%d0%b2%d2%96%d2%a1%d0%93%d1%9e%d0%b2%d2%96%d2%a1%d0%92%c2%ac%d0%93%d2%93%d0%b2%d2%96%d2%a1%d0%93%d3%ae%d0%bf%d2%9d%d2%aa10.hfaw&p_source=&p_type=jump&areatype=","title":"广州当前天气","snippet":"广州空气质量 39 优 0 50 100 150 200 300 500 空气很棒，快出门呼吸新鲜空气吧。 适宜外出","cite_index":null,"published_at":null,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/weathercn.com","site_name":"华风爱科气象科技","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://weather.com/zh-CN/forecast/air-quality/l/37dd90a3a17d6f9942ef56a03373eaa185be2b88164dc31754a305d17d7646c9","title":"越秀区, 广州市, 广东省 空气质量预报 - The Weather Channel | weather.com","snippet":"今日空气质量- 越秀区, 广州市, 广东省 优秀 无健康影响。 主要污染物： PM2.5 (2.5 微米以下细颗粒物) 等级 优秀","cite_index":null,"published_at":null,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/weather.com","site_name":"The Weather Channel","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.aqi.in/in/dashboard/china/guangdong-province/guangzhou/baiyun","title":"Baiyun Air Quality Index (AQI) : Real-Time Air Pollution","snippet":"The current real-time AQI (US) level in Baiyun is 58 (Moderate) due to recent rainfall by 0.01mm/hr. This was last updated 2026-03-05 08:01 (Local Time).","cite_index":null,"published_at":1772640000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/aqi.in","site_name":"AQI.in","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.zq12369.com/environment?city=%e5%b9%bf%e5%b7%9e&tab=city","title":"真气网-关注环境空气质量|广州PM2.5查询|PM2.5实时查询|PM2.5雾霾地图|空气质量地图指数AQI和PM2.5预报查询","snippet":"AQI范围: 40~70 ### 首要污染物: O3,PM2.5 ### 出行建议: 极少数异常敏感人群应减少户外活动 ... AQI范围: 60~90","cite_index":null,"published_at":1774886400.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/zq12369.com","site_name":"真气网","query_indexes":[0]}]}

