data: {"p":"response/fragments/-2/results","v":[{"url":"https://www.weather.com.cn/weather/101280101.shtml","title":"广州天气预报,广州7天天气预报,广州15天天气预报,广州天气查询","snippet":"5日（明天） ... 25℃/20℃ <3级 # 6日（后天） 中雨转多云 30℃/23℃ 3-4级转<3级 # 7日（周二） 雷阵雨转多云 29℃/24℃","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/weather.com.cn","site_name":"天气网","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.nmc.cn/publish/forecast/AGD/guangzhou.html","title":"广州-天气预报","snippet":"04/04 ... 04/05 周日 暴雨 ... 04/06 周一 中雨 ... 04/07 周二 雷阵雨 ... 04/08 周三","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/nmc.cn","site_name":"中央气象台","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.sohu.com/a/1004726143_162758?scm=10001.325_13-325_13.0.0-0-0-0-0.5_1334&spm=smpc.channel_248.block3_308_NDdFbm_1_fd.1.1775175954306LbCjz6t_324","title":"大暴雨、12级大风、冰雹！广州未来7天都“泡汤”","snippet":"广州市气象台预计，4月3日—4日广州有中到大雨局部暴雨，4月5日—6日有大到暴雨，并伴有雷电、短时强降水、8～10级局部11～12级短时大风、局地冰雹等强对流天气。4月7日起降水减弱。","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775145600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/sohu.com","site_name":"Sohu","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://daohuangpuqu.gz-cmc.com/pages/2026/04/04/69ada0e552a245e5b0859954b7ab4cf3.html","title":"广东，要下暴雨、大暴雨了！","snippet":"广州市气象台预计，4月4日广州有中到大雨局部暴雨，4月5日有大到暴雨，并伴有雷电、短时强降水、8～10级短时大风、局地冰雹等强对流天气，4月6日白天起降水逐渐减弱。","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/gz-cmc.com","site_name":"广州日报新花城","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://news.dayoo.com/guangzhou/202604/04/139995_54944458.htm","title":"广州6日雨势减弱，随后迎来一段平稳天气","snippet":"广州市气象台预计，4月5日有大到暴雨，并伴有雷电、短时强降水、6～8级短时大风等强对流天气，4月6日雨势减弱，4月7日转以多云间阴天为主。 广东具体预报...","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/dayoo.com","site_name":"大洋网","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.gz.gov.cn/zt/fxbxaqdx/gg/content/post_10754327.html","title":"清明假期有大到暴雨","snippet":"4月3日—4日广州有中到大雨局部暴雨，4月5日—6日有大到暴雨，并伴有雷电、短时强降水、8～10级局部11～12级短时大风、局地冰雹等强对流天气。4月7日起降水减弱。","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775145600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/gz.gov.cn","site_name":"广州市人民政府门户网站","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.yzqxj.com/guonei/guangdong-guangzhou/7day.html","title":"广州天气预报7天天气","snippet":"2026-04-05 (星期日) 大雨转雷阵雨 21℃ ～ 25℃ 微风 <3级 | 日出06:16 日落18:43 2026-04-06 (星期一) 雷阵雨转多云","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/yzqxj.com","site_name":"Yzqxj","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://guangzhoubaiyun.gz-cmc.com/pages/2026/04/02/e76e4847f66548089ac19908a65c473b.html","title":"清明假期，又开启“倒水”模式","snippet":"广州市气象台预计，4月2日广州有雷阵雨。4月3日—4日有中到大雨局部暴雨，并伴有短时强降水、8～10级局部11～12级短时大风、冰雹等强对流天气。4月5日—6日仍有明显降水伴强对流过程。","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775059200.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/gz-cmc.com","site_name":"广州日报新花城","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.accuweather.com/zh/cn/guangzhou/102255/weather-forecast/102255?type=locality","title":"广州, 广东省, 中国三天天气预报 | AccuWeather","snippet":"上午局部地区有雷雨；部分晴 ... 大部分多云，潮湿，有雷雨 大部分多云，潮湿，有阵雨或雷雨 ... 大部分多云，潮湿，有零星降雨和雷雨","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775059200.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/accuweather.com","site_name":"AccuWeather","query_indexes":[0]}]}

