8℃","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/yzqxj.com","site_name":"Yzqxj","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://news.dayoo.com/guangzhou/202604/04/139995_54944458.htm","title":"广州6日雨势减弱，随后迎来一段平稳天气","snippet":"广州市气象台预计，4月5日有大到暴雨，并伴有雷电、短时强降水、6～8级短时大风等强对流天气，4月6日雨势减弱，4月7日转以多云间阴天为主。 广东具体预报...","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/dayoo.com","site_name":"大洋网","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://news.southcn.com/node_de9aedeec1/2a08783352.shtml","title":"今日降雨集中在广东南部，清明假期全省多地将遭遇强对流天气","snippet":"广州市区，4日，阴天到多云，有中到大雨局部暴雨，气温在20℃—25℃；5日，阴天，有大到暴雨，气温在21℃—25℃；6日，阴天，有中雨，气温在22℃—28℃。","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775232000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/southcn.com","site_name":"南方网","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://guangzhoubaiyun.gz-cmc.com/pages/2026/04/02/e76e4847f66548089ac19908a65c473b.html","title":"清明假期，又开启“倒水”模式","snippet":"4月3日—4日有中到大雨局部暴雨，并伴有短时强降水、8～10级局部11～12级短时大风、冰雹等强对流天气。4月5日—6日仍有明显降水伴强对流过程。","cite_index":null,"published_at":1775059200.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/gz-cmc.com","site_name":"广州日报新花城","query_indexes":[0]}]}

